"```sql\nSELECT races.year, AVG(CAST(SUBSTR(results.time, 1, INSTR(results.time, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 60 + \n                      CAST(SUBSTR(results.time, INSTR(results.time, ':') + 1) AS REAL)) AS avg_champion_time_seconds\nFROM results\nINNER JOIN races ON results.raceId = races.raceId\nWHERE results.positionOrder = 1 AND races.year < 1975 AND results.time IS NOT NULL\nGROUP BY races.year;\n```"